snippet.title: All 4 in 1 Sachen Multicarts Game Boy (4B-001 - 4B-009)
snippet.description:
Gameplay from all 4 in 1 Sachen multicarts for Nintendo Game Boy.
4B-001, 4B-002, 4B-003, 4B-004, 4B-005, 4B-006, 4B-007, 4B-008 and 4B-009.

Sachen, also known as Thin Chen Enterprise, Commin (on handheld games only) was a Taiwanese developer and publisher of unlicensed games for the NES/Famicom, Game Boy and Mega Drive/Genesis, and licensed games for the Mega Duck and Supervision handhelds.

Origin: Taipei, Taiwan
Years: 1988-early 2007

Consoles: NES/Famicom, Genesis/Mega Drive, Game Boy, Game Boy Color, Mega Duck, Supervision
